				<ext:value>description-en:
This lobby card for the 1978 released Hindi movie &quot;Satyam Shivam Sundaram&quot; shows the lead cast, Zeenat Aman and Shashi Kapoor with a palm tree in the background. She is wearing a veil which he is holding smilingly with his left hand. (gs)</ext:value>
			</ext:item>
